Hostess Brands Inc: Company Profile - Bloomberg



































































  









Feedback
















hostess brands inc
Public Company









Company Profile
Sector: Consumer Staples
Industry: Consumer Products
Sub-Industry: Packaged Food
Hostess Brands, Inc. provides packaged foods. The Company develops, manufactures, markets, sells and distributes baked sweet goods. Hostess Brands offers its products throughout the United States.




